<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您真的能帮我吗？”悟空问弥勒佛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄眉大王很厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用一块布抓走了所有人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还把我关进了金铙里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能打败黄眉大王。”弥勒佛说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他曾经是我的弟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那块布和金铙都是珍贵的佛教宝物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从我这里偷走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我......把那个金铙打碎了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48756</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛笑了。“那个你不用担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得抓住黄眉大王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要把我的计划告诉你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58049</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又来到寺院门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄眉大王！”他喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你如果不放了唐僧他们，我就毁了你整座山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门一下子打开了。黄眉大王走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么敢威胁我？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道我有多厉害吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不厉害。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只是有那块布，就以为自己很厉害而已。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果没有它，你一定会害怕跟我打。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不怕你。”妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回到里面，一会儿又出来了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107399</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>手里拿着一个很重的木棒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107400</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪朝悟空冲过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐！他们的兵器撞了又撞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一边和妖怪打，一边一点点后退。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把妖怪慢慢地引到远离寺院的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们就打到了山下的山谷里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又朝黄眉大王挥了一下金箍棒后，假装害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你太厉害了！”悟空大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我再也不能和你打了！”说完转身跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”黄眉大王大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157482</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你回来，胆小鬼！”妖怪跑着去追悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跑过树林，朝香瓜田跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王追过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在哪儿，悟空？”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，妖怪看见了很多的香瓜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他舔了舔嘴唇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些香瓜看起来很好吃。”他自言自语说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个农夫正在附近干活儿。他的肚子很大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190472</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，农夫！”黄眉大王喊了一声，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190473</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给我一个香瓜！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>农夫放下钉耙，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝妖怪走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我给你挑个熟透的香瓜吧。”农夫看了看地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他拿起一个熟透的香瓜。“给你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王拿起香瓜想吃一口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217634</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，那个香瓜缩成了野草莓大小，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从他手中跳出来，跳进了他的嗓子眼儿。咕噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪捂住了肚子。“呃！香瓜是怎么回事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在妖怪肚子里，悟空拳打脚踢。嘣！砰！嘣！砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”黄眉大王大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他发现农夫不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛站在他旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛瞪着妖怪。“把我的布交出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，是，师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王从袍子里拿出布，递给了弥勒佛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你可以出来了，悟空。”弥勒佛说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272151</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小悟空从妖怪的鼻子里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛把那块布扔向黄眉大王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285201</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布包住妖怪后，变小了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛把布放进了衣兜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空变回原形。他和弥勒佛回到寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296749</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>弥勒佛念咒语，金铙自己就变回了原样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他微笑着对悟空说：“祝你好运！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他就不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316071</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空帮大家解开了绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316072</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亢金龙、乌龟，还有大蛇谢过悟空后，飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，悟空。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你提醒我小心时，我没相信，对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。“总有一天，您会相信我的，师父！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>师徒四人走到外面，继续朝西边走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>